Boasting edible leaves, '''silvergrass''', more commonly known by the derogatory name of '''goatgrass''',<ref name="Strongholds" /> was the predominant form of ground flora on the plains of [[Kinyen/Legends|Kinyen]]. It had a silver sheen to its green [[Color/Legends|color]], and gave off a sweet aroma.

A favorite food among [[Gran/Legends|Gran]], it was also used in more mundane cooking, as when [[Porcellus/Legends|Porcellus]] would present goatgrass-stuffed [[gamwidge]] to [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|his master]]. It was also used in [[goatgrass salad]] served on [[Malastare/Legends|Malastare]] and in [[Dex's Diner/Legends|Dex's Diner]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] used shipments of goatgrass bound for [[Ree-Yees/Legends|Ree-Yees]], to smuggle the necessary components for a [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonator]] with which to kill his master, Jabba the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]].

